  "text": "Amongst these pollutants, phenolic compounds are notorious, hence their toxicity towards human and animal organisms. These molecules are nonetheless highly versatile concerning industrial use and are employed in polyamide production by textile industries [CITATION_1] , as well as a plethora of other applications [CITATION_2] .",
